TEAM BRETT SWARM ROBOTICS

How to operate code


Setup

Step 1: roscd stage

Step 2: make

Step 3: roscd Project2Sample

Step 4: rosmake


Running

Step 1: roscd Project2Sample/bin

Step 2: ./Launcher X

(X is the number of robots you want to run)


Testing

Step 1: rostest Project2Sample RXTestSuite.test
